@startuml
title Diagrama de Secuencia - Crear Asignatura (Spring Boot + React)

actor "Docente" as Teacher
participant "Frontend (React)" as FE
participant "AsignaturasController" as Controller
participant "AsignaturaService" as Service
participant "AsignaturaRepository" as Repo
database "Base de Datos (PostgreSQL)" as DB

Teacher -> FE: Clic en "Nueva Asignatura"
activate FE
FE --> Teacher: Mostrar Formulario (datos mínimos)
Teacher -> FE: Ingresa datos (título, código, curso académico)
FE -> FE: Validar formulario (client-side)
FE -> Controller: POST /api/asignaturas (AsignaturaCreateDTO JSON)\n(Header: Authorization: Bearer <token>)
activate Controller
Controller -> Controller: extraer docenteId del JWT
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: crearAsignatura(asignaturaCreateDTO, docenteId)
activate Service
Service -> Service: Mapear DTO a Entidad
Service -> Service: Asociar asignatura al docente (docenteId)
Service -> Repo: save(asignatura)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB: INSERT INTO asignaturas (titulo, codigo, curso_academico, docente_id) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?)
activate DB
DB --> Repo: Asignatura (con ID generado)
deactivate DB
Repo --> Service: Asignatura
deactivate Repo
Service --> Controller: AsignaturaDTO (201 Created)
deactivate Service
deactivate Controller
Controller --> FE: 201 Created (AsignaturaDTO JSON)
deactivate Controller
FE -> FE: Mostrar Toast "Asignatura creada correctamente"
FE -> FE: Redirigir a editarAsignatura(asignaturaNueva)
FE --> Teacher: Mostrar Formulario de Edición
deactivate FE

alt Datos Inválidos
    Controller --> FE: 400 Bad Request (validation errors)
    deactivate Controller
    FE --> Teacher: Mostrar errores de validación
end

@enduml